─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CHARACTER CONTENT ATTRIBUTIONS
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Quote content in characters/*/character.json files is derived from or
inspired by verified public sources as documented in the _sources[] field
of each character.json file. These attributions are for reference and
transparency only.

• Beavis and Butt-Head: © Mike Judge / MTV / Comedy Central (1993–2024)
• King James Bible (1611): Public domain
• Maynard James Keenan quotes: verified from BrainyQuote, Wikiquote,
  A Perfect Union of Contrary Things (Hal Leonard, 2016)
• Jonathan Davis quotes: verified from Metal Hammer, Blabbermouth,
  Rolling Stone
• Brian "Head" Welch quotes: from Save Me from Myself (HarperOne, 2007)
  and verified interviews

